OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,FA targeted vaccination programme will
OL,8,Froll out for students living in halls
OL,9,Fat the University of Kent after an
OL,10,F"unprecedented" outbreak of meningitis.
OL,12,F15 cases of meningitis have so far
OL,13,Fbeen reported to the UK Health
OL,14,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA), including two
OL,15,Fdeaths.
OL,17,FThe agency said all 15 cases had
OL,18,Frequired hospital admission, with four
OL,19,Fcases confirmed to be meningitis B.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]
