CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773933104
OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,FAround 5,000 students in university
OL,8,Fhalls in Kent are to be offered the
OL,9,FmenB vaccine in the coming days.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, Health Secretary Wes
OL,12,FStreeting said most students would not
OL,13,Falready be vaccinated against menB.
OL,15,FHe told MPs that the outbreak is
OL,16,F"unprecedented" and is "a rapidly
OL,17,Fdeveloping situation".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@OO]xD@XOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773933104
OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,FMr Streeting said the menB vaccine has
OL,8,Fbeen available on the NHS since 2015
OL,9,Fas part of routine childhood
OL,10,Fimmunisations.
OL,12,FHe added that "clearly most students
OL,13,Fwould not be vaccinated".
OL,15,FMr Streeting said: "Given the severity
OL,16,Fof the situation, I can confirm to the
OL,17,FHouse that we will begin a targeted
OL,18,Fvaccination programme for students
OL,19,Fliving in halls of residence at the
OL,20,FUniversity of Kent in Canterbury,
OL,21,Fwhich will begin in the coming days."
OL,26,@tD@OOUuD@XO]wD@TOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
