PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773933104
OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,FThe programme may also expand further
OL,8,Fif other groups are deemed to be at
OL,9,Frisk.UKHSA chief executive Susan
OL,10,FHopkins said the outbreak looks like
OL,11,F"a super-spreader event, with ongoing
OL,12,Fspread within the halls of residence
OL,13,Fin the universities".
OL,15,FShe said: "I can say that in my 35
OL,16,Fyears working in medicine, in
OL,17,Fhealthcare and hospitals, this is the
OL,18,Fmost cases I've seen in a single
OL,19,Fweekend with this type of infection.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@TO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
