PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773933104
OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,F"It's the explosive nature that is
OL,8,Funprecedented here ` the number of
OL,9,Fcases in such a short space of time."
OL,11,FFour schools across Kent have now
OL,12,Fconfirmed cases and hundreds of people
OL,13,Fare being offered antibiotics as an
OL,14,Fimmediate treatment.
OL,16,FAll reported cases so far have a link
OL,17,Fto Kent, according to the UKHSA.At
OL,18,Fleast one person who fell ill and had
OL,19,Flinks to Kent attended a hospital in
OL,20,FLondon.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@eO]
