OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,FEarlier on Tuesday, the deputy
OL,8,Fdirector of the immunisation and
OL,9,Fvaccine preventable diseases division
OL,10,Fat the UKHSA, Dr Gayatri
OL,11,FAmirthalingam, said the outbreak of
OL,12,Fmeningitis had been "unusual", but she
OL,13,Fdid not believe there was a current
OL,14,Frisk to anyone outside the Kent region.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the headteacher at Queen
OL,17,FElizabeth's Grammar School in
OL,18,FFaversham paid tribute to year 13
OL,19,Fpupil named locally as Juliette Kenny,
OL,20,Fwho died at the weekend from the
OL,21,Finfection.
OL,26,@tD@UOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
