OL,3,CStudents in halls in Kent to be
OL,4,Coffered meningitis B vaccine over
OL,5,Ccoming days
OL,7,FThose who attended Club Chemistry
OL,8,Fbetween these dates can collect
OL,9,Fantibiotics from: the Gate Clinic at
OL,10,FKent and Canterbury Hospital; Westgate
OL,11,FHall on Westgate Hall Road,
OL,12,FCanterbury; the Carey Building, Thanet
OL,13,FHub, Margate Northwood Road; and the
OL,14,FSenate building at the University of
OL,15,FKent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
